去攻擊反修例既人。<br />\n我地要做既係得到輿論支持去統一壓逼政府。<br />\n你塞地鐵只會引起越黎越多人對反送中既人反感而少左個政治籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n利申非三毛 天滅中共"},{"pid":"c3eb77fe77bd5f15975ea856b7c544ebd2dd49ad","tid":1197200,"uid":54220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:47:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fa664c2d28d9859e6c9c52e11f6a58846055df4","tid":1197200,"uid":217300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc40ec4289bc1eec258a1cc2bfbfb4df32ccdd7","tid":1197200,"uid":119330,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"睇黎佔中後<br />\n仲有好多人無反思 點解最後失敗<br />\n以及之後本土派 港獨派<br />\n點解會失民心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"係，咁你有咩高見"},{"pid":"b2925a01e2f6316e26d80fecf81f1c88d97b86ac","tid":1197200,"uid":10114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf3069c13725b927e9b55af197cf71f661cbeafc","tid":1197200,"uid":86416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n［撘地鐵小tips］琴日地鐵好塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1197520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1197520</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2. 太多人個時就唔好行入車箱，頂住到門架車會開唔到<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果見到人唔小心跌咗野落路軌要向職員報告<br />\n有障礙物係路軌好危險，你知地鐵唔係無試過出軌<br />\n<br />\n4. 根據《車票發出條件》，所有乘客進入已付車費區域後，須在入閘後150分鐘內完成車程，並透過出閘機離開已付車費區域。<br />\n<br />\n天氣咁熱去到目的地未夠鐘可以係站內嘆下冷氣先，唔好中暑呀<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果返工時間人多，覺得有唔舒服都可以向職員求助<br />\n有時有啲病可大可小，例如Premature ventricular contractions (PVC)<br />\n<br />\n佢係心律不正既其中一種，會突然間覺得心口痛/唔舒服<br />\n除非個一刻即刻做心電圖，否則之後都未必查證到你有無事<br />\n<br />\n遇到咁既情況，你可能會好驚，頭暈，行唔到<br />\n記住唔好夾硬起身周圍郁增加心臟負荷<br />\n最好就叫職員比你原地休息一陣"},{"pid":"4658d77dee1a388bb4b7c7252324f09c9aa1297d","tid":1197200,"uid":29978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"發夢見到有個肥婆係地鐵第一卡唔小心撞開左駕駛室度門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />站務主任上車搞左好耐架車先開得番"},{"pid":"41c3448daf28f3e37ae1f32af092acf957760b09","tid":1197200,"uid":160589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"如果千幾人都係地鐵站到等人會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a23db2fd8b7a620eb4d8d0a1cefecd7cf6aed9","tid":1197200,"uid":217954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"係就快<br />\n唔好等下個禮拜"},{"pid":"f9685d2550ea6da037e4ff49bdb1379e98c2a508","tid":1197200,"uid":233316,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"唔好咁小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9d95eb25c737338b0aac435930fa623c4f5dcb","tid":1197200,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"840c063129df6739520f53bee70a7d2ce8f1e626","tid":1197200,"uid":92479,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"熄抽氣冷氣就收你皮啦，係站外都重得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"佢咁做即刻可以俾傳媒話佢哋政治逼害"},{"pid":"ffc382938c3038be089d5366c5a1be210d354856","tid":1197200,"uid":195004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de89fa8a60e203c4c3b6515e11bc7c90b75e339","tid":1197200,"uid":252404,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"quote":{"pid":"32058abcdd9cf77f263d657f4a2d038c3007d96e","tid":1197200,"uid":158411,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"急屎點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"急屎就咁落個站痾<br />\n大把人想涼冷氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"唔啦，佢班閪樣咁鍾意支港融合同包容呀嘛，做d野比佢地包容下"},{"pid":"fc2cda9cf6c4ccd90f927c0586b434d4529a1fe7","tid":1197200,"uid":3716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"其實幾有計<br />\n不過肯做埋呢啲嘅嘢得啲有種嘅人<br />\n而數目只可以迫兩架車廂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{