r />\n<br />\n天氣咁熱去到目的地未夠鐘可以係站內嘆下冷氣先，唔好中暑呀<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果返工時間人多，覺得有唔舒服都可以向職員求助<br />\n有時有啲病可大可小，例如Premature ventricular contractions (PVC)<br />\n<br />\n佢係心律不正既其中一種，會突然間覺得心口痛/唔舒服<br />\n除非個一刻即刻做心電圖，否則之後都未必查證到你有無事<br />\n<br />\n遇到咁既情況，你可能會好驚，頭暈，行唔到<br />\n記住唔好夾硬起身周圍郁增加心臟負荷<br />\n最好就叫職員比你原地休息一陣<br />\n<br />\n有其他tips可以再加"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:30:12.000Z","msg":"3.<br />\n冇帶八達通記得買車飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ea78662d7ac3704a111a21f9271412a87f4c93","tid":1197200,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26c508daae5c80300eb34a9c2c8d2918398c95c8","tid":1197200,"uid":252404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"弱智， 港鐵熄冷氣即迫到你落車， 琴晚金鐘站咪係咁， 熄冷氣焗到仆街"},{"pid":"2d7d8c2acb27b851af7442b4886726ffe76795a6","tid":1197200,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"325be77c1560faac6f20c3f36ee5bff9b7c33c50","tid":1197200,"uid":185373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"仲慘 果班想黎幫手既 無地鐵坐"},{"pid":"b3f23dbd0231f9e160d9c5c1499c2a9ce047aa87","tid":1197200,"uid":111181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8791def619b4fc78252f0e2b67add48e86e2eebb","tid":1197200,"uid":155682,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間響應地鐵安全上落扶手梯, 左右各企一人唔行, 成段時間剩係上上落落咁都夠, 之後去下個站出閘, 好似唔過唔記得幾耐係計1個站錢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"120分鐘"},{"pid":"3da957359573c4ee07b9cac69ea96a0d9497ac7f","tid":1197200,"uid":108224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dc4be374c8625e9177c2f1b24e059c2ac160e81","tid":1197200,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d7d5e36596e9f1dd175b1fecd72ba8b9e3cf4fe","tid":1197200,"uid":23988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bc4